{"tid":1754709,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[王立強案]  正要離境時被調查局約談 中国創新投資向心、龔青原來在台灣","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T02:45:17.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e3b1d9f6b94e93b9208e0ee9155759a754478820","tid":1754709,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:54:55.000Z","msg":"正要離境時被調查局約談 向心、龔青原來在台灣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/11/25/n11678915.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F19%2F11%2F25%2Fn11678915.htm&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJq%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=cce81f54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/11/25/n11678915.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2019年11月25日訊】香港上市公司「中國創新投資(<a href=\"http://01217.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01217.HK&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJq%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=a3cafa3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01217.HK</a>)」執行董事、主席兼行政總裁向心和替任董事龔青，因被投誠澳洲的中共特工王立強指為中共從事間諜活動，被調查局桃園市調查處發出通知書，要求就新聞報道事宜配合調查，兩人已聘請台灣律師提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n自稱是中共特工的王立強，十月向澳洲反間諜機關投誠，澳洲媒體23日刊出其訪談。王立強聲稱，他以中央軍事委員會聯合參謀部創建的香港上市公司「中國創新投資」員工的身分，在該公司主席向心及其妻、該公司候補董事龔青的指揮下，透過金錢收買、利誘與恐嚇威脅等手段，針對澳洲、香港及台灣等民主社會，進行大規模的滲透。<br />\n<br />\n「中國創新投資」25日發出通知，表示公司收到向心和龔青的通知，他們在桃園機場正要離境時，收到調查局桃園市調查處發出通知書，要求就新聞報道事宜配合調查，兩人已聘請台灣律師提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n台灣知名政論家汪浩23日在臉書貼文指出，香港上市公司「中國創新投資」「根據CIIL公司文件，該公司從事『軍事和民用部門整合』的投資。公司替任董事龔青，即為董事長向心的妻子，龔青曾在兩家政府機構任職，其中之一是人民解放軍的情報組織『中國國防科技信息中心』。」<br />\n<br />\n汪浩還特別貼出 CIIL在2015年的股價圖。 根據該公司年報，該公司專注對香港上市公司進行短期投資。他表示，截至2018年12月31日止年度，投資之銷售所得款總額為2億3421萬港元（2017年：7億2900.8萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n汪浩指出，這家公司年報兩年賺近10億港幣，如此的獲利，股價卻是1分6毫港幣，市值2億港幣。他說，「大家有看過這麼賺錢的公司有這麼奇怪的股價圖嗎？」"},{"pid":"acc5d0bbd24f84972c88721022698df47c824991","tid":1754709,"uid":254235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:01:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4eb5199e1968425bf74e4f489634dbaa5efd404e","tid":1754709,"uid":140949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6a4345d40c2f7f436a835c0f1ee08d664cee62","tid":1754709,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1277fb2b7c86ea7ce0a24e5a15b0af1e16c5702c","tid":1754709,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推上熱門：新戰線&mdash;用建制方法贏建制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"36a4631d86f1ee2e3ff6d28509a1d207f38b4967","tid":1754709,"uid":60200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:40:00.000Z","msg":"食花生"},{"pid":"d8bb885b1ea75b7ce5f036f5dc8d25f3267c1680","tid":1754709,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:04:44.000Z","msg":"好撚醒"},{"pid":"91c78faf25b4cdd694f9ff66568a369245f5264b","tid":1754709,"uid":311004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:07:07.000Z","msg":"留名跟進下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b29d9125381587abe480397a757a7dba6172d3","tid":1754709,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:29:44.000Z","msg":"唔好俾佢哋走"},{"pid":"01db6a45d5d9b5e934b869ace05a1b557d6a7df9","tid":1754709,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:43:01.000Z","msg":"斷正<br />\n成個情報部摺埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5f4810cd51ea8316e825801aed1080f8c96893","tid":1754709,"uid":90883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:44:12.000Z","msg":"走得咁急 坐多陣先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea2be376379441965fef0461d0d86c91c39c033","tid":1754709,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ba42929df2f1fa72c414c573d209d268ec9b5e","tid":1754709,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:38:01.000Z","msg":"去台灣做咩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e20f33db5071d884760429bc622007460984ff7","tid":1754709,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:41:12.000Z","msg":"又會噉啱喺台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9fb5e5e0dbdc7f84cdfc570c23b646cb7837fd","tid":1754709,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:50:36.000Z","msg":"咁啱就黎大選，咁啱係台灣，咁啱一比人爆料就走，乜咁啱呀"},{"pid":"abe7087c7140b3c9cb972a058e8a9c819928b9dd","tid":1754709,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c26f73492b623e440a3515b4dd68aa0443550a","tid":1754709,"uid":131551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:56:40.000Z","msg":"真係笑撚死 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭一個蝴蝶效應   搞死中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9076d33eb04ae9c62878d72b36d13209c4bde4","tid":1754709,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:45:17.000Z","msg":"中國創新向心夫婦涉國安法 北檢限制出境出海<br />\n最新更新：2019/11/26 07:43<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j3KXXpH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj3KXXpH.jpg&h=92739325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法務部調查局國家安全維護處幹員25日在桃園機場攔下來台之後欲出境的中國創新投資公司執行董事向心及替任董事龔青（前低頭者），台北地檢署26日凌晨諭令2人限制出境出海。中央社記者郭日曉攝 108年11月25日<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者林長順台北26日電）自稱中國間諜的男子王立強日前指控香港中國創新投資公司主席向心吸納他做間諜。調查局24日在桃園機場攔下欲出境的向心、龔青夫婦。台北地檢署今天凌晨諭令2人限制出境出海。<br />\n<br />\n王立強向外媒指出，總部位在香港德輔道西的中國創新投資是在中國人民解放軍總參謀部之下成立，為的是「滲透香港的金融市場並蒐集軍事情報」。<br />\n<br />\n他並稱，中國創新投資在台灣媒體業投下經費，與電視台建立秘密的聯盟，讓中國可以控制這些媒體，遂行新聞檢查。<br />\n<br />\n調查局及國安局針對外媒報導，分頭進行查證，調查局國家安全維護處幹員24日在桃園機場攔下欲出境的向心及龔青，帶回訊問，昨天晚間依違反國家安全法移送北檢。<br />\n<br />\n北檢特別安排位於信義路一段、前特偵組所在地的第五辦公室偵訊，檢察官訊問後，今天凌晨2時許諭令2人限制出境、出海。（編輯：張佑之）1081126"}]}